author: Xbox
description:
Prepare for a mind-blowing co-op adventure! Split Fiction arrives March 6, 2025. 

https://www.xbox.com/games/store/split-fiction/9N1WXXD1RL8D

Jump into a split-screen adventure that's tailored for two. You and a friend will coordinate your actions and timing as you work together to overcome a variety of challenges. Split Fiction is coming to you from Hazelight – the co-op thrill-makers that brought you It Takes Two and A Way Out – so you know there'll be some wild surprises in store.

Invite a friend to play with you for free on any platform with the Friend’s Pass*! As long as one of you owns the game, you can both play.

*Friend’s Pass requires installation of the Friend’s Pass and applicable platform account. Online play requires a friend on any platform. One user must own the full game in order for the co-op player to play the full game.
